Ziving — what this is
=====================
Private Zcash fundraising pages — like JustGiving, with a z.

Fundraisers create a campaign page, receive shielded ZEC straight to their
own wallet, and show live gifts on the page or an OBS stream overlay.
Ziving never holds spend keys: donors pay the campaign address wallet-to-
wallet. There are no accounts, no KYC, and no cause checks — pages are
unverified by design.

Pricing (prepaid in ZEC memo quotes):
  • UFVK scanning credit — $0.10 / day (grace ~1.5 days at create)
  • Homepage feature      — $5.00 / day (optional, 1–30 days)

Site: https://ziving.org
API:  https://mcp.winbit32.com/v1/ziving
MCP:  https://mcp.winbit32.com/mcp  (tools winbit32_ziving_*)
